Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.77,0:00:08.32,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,How did it come to this?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.78,0:00:12.82,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,In that moment, all I wanted was to hold her close.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.53,0:00:18.95,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,This tiny little Humanoid felt right at home right there in my arms.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.95,0:00:23.21,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Like she was the most precious thing in the world...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.00,0:00:30.76,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Calm down! Calm down, dammit! This is {\i1}Atri{\i0} we're talking about!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.76,0:00:33.09,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,The dictionary definition of hardware failure!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.09,0:00:37.34,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Natsuki-san, do it right...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.14,0:00:41.10,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,My back teeth won't brush themselves...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.47,0:00:44.85,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,It's temporary insanity. It's gotta be!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.15,0:00:47.10,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.10,0:00:49.61,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Hey! Wake up, Atri!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.61,0:00:53.44,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,You have to reach waaay back...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.44,0:00:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck kind of dream are you having?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.86,0:00:57.62,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Actually, wait...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.62,0:00:59.20,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,You have dreams?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.54,0:01:06.96,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Natsuki-san, you dirty boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.85,0:02:48.31,Default,Saki,0,0,0,,Sensei, I solved it...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.56,0:02:51.81,Default,Saki,0,0,0,,Sensei?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.81,0:02:53.77,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Well, it {\i1}is{\i0} awfully hot today.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.77,0:02:56.86,Default,Yoko,0,0,0,,Yeah, totally... like that explains anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.86,0:02:57.74,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,It doesn't?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.74,0:03:03.41,Default,Ryuji,0,0,0,,{\i1}Something{\i0} happened, that's for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.41,0:03:05.03,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.03,0:03:09.62,Default,Yoko,0,0,0,,Us girls know how to keep things zipped up, but guys are an open book when they get like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.96,0:03:10.92,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.92,0:03:13.50,Default,Yoko,0,0,0,,Yup. And don't you forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.50,0:03:17.55,Default,Yoko,0,0,0,,Ain't no guy in the world who can pull the wool over a woman's eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.84,0:03:23.18,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,Have fun, kiddos!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.18,0:03:25.89,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,But don't swim too far out, you hear?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.31,0:03:30.52,Default,Ririka,0,0,0,,Sensei! Atrin went under and isn't coming back up!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.81,0:03:31.73,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.52,0:03:36.77,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,I found a crab!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.82,0:03:39.28,Default,Miyo,0,0,0,,That's a hermit crab...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.07,0:03:47.37,Default,Ryuji,0,0,0,,Man, he's really got it bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.87,0:03:49.12,Default,Ryuji,0,0,0,,Whoa, whoa, whoa!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.08,0:03:53.29,Default,Yoko,0,0,0,,Something happen, buddy? \NWith a certain Atri-chan, perhaps?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.71,0:03:54.75,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,N-No.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.92,0:03:58.88,Default,Yoko,0,0,0,,Whoa, your ears are burning up! Aren't you just too precious!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.80,0:04:02.22,Default,Ryuji,0,0,0,,For real?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.22,0:04:05.43,Default,Ryuji,0,0,0,,So you finally got over your denial that Atri was your first love?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.84,0:04:06.93,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.93,0:04:07.81,Default,Yoko,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.81,0:04:09.68,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,"Well" what?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.68,0:04:12.69,Default,Yoko,0,0,0,,Did you maybe, just maybe take your relationship to the next level?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.69,0:04:17.98,Default,Ryuji,0,0,0,,Get back here, Natsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.73,0:04:21.74,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,It's got nothing to do with you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.11,0:04:23.11,Default,Ryuji,0,0,0,,Sure it does, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.11,0:04:23.74,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.74,0:04:27.99,Default,Yoko,0,0,0,,You heard him. Stop dragging this out and spill it already.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.40,0:04:32.79,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,I told you already. Nothing happened, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.79,0:04:34.75,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Go find something else to gossip about.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.75,0:04:35.33,Default,Yoko,0,0,0,,But—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.71,0:04:37.54,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Let's just drop it, all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.54,0:04:40.25,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,He said nothing happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.09,0:04:44.17,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Sorry, Natsu-kun. How 'bout we all go join the kids for a swim?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.51,0:04:47.51,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Fine, I give up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.74,0:04:48.60,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.14,0:04:52.22,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,And here I was trying to forget all about it...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.22,0:04:55.27,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,I'll tell you, but don't get the wrong idea about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.98,0:04:59.15,Default,Yoko; Ryuji; Minamo,0,0,0,,You kissed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.15,0:05:00.11,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,You were the ones who asked! {i honesty don't know what to do with this lol}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.11,0:05:02.32,Default,Yoko,0,0,0,,I mean, yeah, but still...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.32,0:05:05.86,Default,Ryuji,0,0,0,,Hell yeah, Natsu! I always knew you had it in you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.86,0:05:07.03,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Knock it off!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.03,0:05:08.49,Default,Ryuji,0,0,0,,C'mon, don't be shy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.49,0:05:11.95,Default,Ryuji,0,0,0,,Getting together with your first love? That's every guy's dream, dude!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.95,0:05:14.50,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,I told you not to get the wrong idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.50,0:05:15.99,Default,Ryuji,0,0,0,,What's the big deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.04,0:05:16.94,Default,Yoko,0,0,0,,Bruhhhhh...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.94,0:05:17.71,Default,Ryuji,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.13,0:05:19.71,Default,Yoko,0,0,0,,Holy cringe...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.04,0:05:21.05,Default,Ryuji,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.05,0:05:24.67,Default,Yoko,0,0,0,,You heard me! How old do you think this guy is, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.67,0:05:26.63,Default,Yoko,0,0,0,,Dude's {\i1}seventeen!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.63,0:05:31.39,Default,Yoko,0,0,0,,And he's in love with {\i1}Atri-chan?{\i0} That's gotta be statutor—
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.35,0:05:32.39,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,What part of "it's not like that" do you not understand?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.64,0:05:34.14,Default,Ryuji,0,0,0,,But you kissed her, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.14,0:05:37.14,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,That was, uh... a coincidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.14,0:05:39.44,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Or maybe a case of temporary insanity...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.44,0:05:42.11,Default,Yoko,0,0,0,,Yeah, buddy. I'm sure the judge is gonna love those excuses. {not sure what to do here either}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.11,0:05:43.94,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,What do you even want from me?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.94,0:05:46.86,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Stop overreacting and just think about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.86,0:05:50.28,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Atri's a Humanoid. You shouldn't think of her like an ordinary human.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.53,0:05:54.54,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,But you were the one who said she might have a heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.54,0:05:59.54,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,And if that's true, she deserves to be treated like the rest of us...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.83,0:06:01.88,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Well... yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.88,0:06:06.17,Default,Yoko,0,0,0,,Either way, the elephant in the room you've been avoiding is how you actually feel about her!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.17,0:06:07.80,Default,Yoko,0,0,0,,Well? You love her or not?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.72,0:06:12.85,Default,Yoko,0,0,0,,I ain't hearing a "no" from you, buddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.22,0:06:16.60,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,To be honest... I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.93,0:06:18.35,Default,Yoko,0,0,0,,You're not sure?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.52,0:06:26.65,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,In my mind, Atri's a Humanoid... but she's also my first love...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.11,0:06:30.32,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,It's all so confusing, I don't know how to make sense of it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.70,0:06:32.41,Default,Yoko,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.41,0:06:35.95,Default,Ryuji,0,0,0,,Well, now that you put it that way, I can get where you're coming from.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.95,0:06:40.00,Default,Ryuji,0,0,0,,Until just the other day, she was just a Humanoid who fell into your life outta nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.00,0:06:42.08,Default,Ryuji,0,0,0,,But then she suddenly morphs into your long-lost crush?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.34,0:06:45.21,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,There you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.21,0:06:46.84,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Natsuki-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.84,0:06:47.59,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.88,0:06:52.09,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Catherine said sneaking out of class is bad!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.09,0:06:54.39,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,We're all supposed to be swimming right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.39,0:06:56.39,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,You know I can't swim.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.89,0:07:01.69,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Catherine said there's ways to practice swimming, even with a prosthetic!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.69,0:07:04.36,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Leave it to me and my high specs!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.36,0:07:06.40,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Taking a dip with a toaster like you? Count me out. {!}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.40,0:07:08.19,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,I value my life far too highly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.19,0:07:10.49,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Officers! Take this man away!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.57,0:07:12.41,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Ahh, where's my whistle?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.37,0:07:15.78,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Heh, figures. My calculator probably has more RAM than you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.78,0:07:17.66,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Argh, that's that last straw!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.66,0:07:20.00,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Taste my super roundhouse rocket punch!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.00,0:07:22.37,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Oh, a new move? Go on, hit me with your best shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.37,0:07:24.67,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Super roundhouse rocket—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.38,0:07:28.34,Default,Ririka; Toru; Miyo,0,0,0,,Bye-bye!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.34,0:07:30.38,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,See you tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.92,0:07:33.01,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Talk about anything interesting today?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.01,0:07:36.89,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Yes. I learned about the theory of relativity.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.89,0:07:37.93,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,From Ririka?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.39,0:07:41.23,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,She really means it, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.23,0:07:44.69,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,About attending the Academy one day, and about setting the world to right. {戻す, tricky}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.69,0:07:46.65,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,It really reminds me of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.78,0:07:52.32,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Oh, Atri-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.32,0:07:53.11,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.11,0:07:56.74,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,If you want to do it tonight, you should probably go on ahead and start prepping,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.74,0:07:57.95,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,TM,or it'll take too long. {retime these two lines imo, splitting is weird}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.95,0:08:00.20,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Huh? But...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.20,0:08:02.16,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Do as Minamo says.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.16,0:08:03.87,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.87,0:08:07.71,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Look forward to it, Natsuki-san! I'll be giving you a taste of mom's cooking tonight!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.67,0:08:11.88,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Mom's cooking?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.22,0:08:16.60,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,I taught her a new dish. She's getting pretty good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.55,0:08:19.01,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Looks like it, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.35,0:08:22.77,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,She really wants you to be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.27,0:08:25.77,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,She says that would make her happy, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.11,0:08:33.61,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,You know, I think you were right all along. I think Atri-chan really does have a heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.61,0:08:38.49,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,I don't think an AI could possibly say something with that much feeling behind it.{Bad news, Minamo.}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.16,0:08:43.04,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,So you should be true to your own heart...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.04,0:08:48.04,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,And make sure you let her know how you really feel, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.67,0:08:51.05,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,I know you can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.96,0:08:53.17,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Minamo...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.26,0:08:57.97,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,I'm rooting for you, Natsu-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.97,0:08:59.05,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,See you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.70,0:09:19.07,Default,Ryuji,0,0,0,,You sure about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.07,0:09:19.70,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.70,0:09:22.24,Default,Yoko,0,0,0,,Sorry. We were eavesdropping.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.24,0:09:25.66,Default,Yoko,0,0,0,,You know you're shooting yourself in the foot, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.33,0:09:28.50,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Yeah. Guess I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.50,0:09:30.46,Default,Ryuji,0,0,0,,And you're okay with that?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.84,0:09:38.34,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,When Natsu-kun went to the Academy, I didn't cry at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.01,0:09:43.14,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Good luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.14,0:09:43.97,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.56,0:09:48.19,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,I knew I was going to miss him,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.44,0:09:54.78,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,but it made me even happier knowing he was taking a big step towards his dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.99,0:09:59.24,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,As I watched him walk away,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.78,0:10:03.74,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,I realized I also needed to do everything I could, right here.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.04,0:10:13.05,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Natsu-kun was so young when he lost both his mom and his leg,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.46,0:10:16.97,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,but he still studied so hard all on his own,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.92,0:10:22.26,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,never losing sight of his dream to get the world moving again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.06,0:10:27.18,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,I don't want to {\i1}be with{\i0} him...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.89,0:10:32.02,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,I want to do my best alongside him.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.69,0:10:35.32,Default,Ryuji,0,0,0,,But—
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.32,0:10:36.23,Default,Yoko,0,0,0,,Quiet, you!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.70,0:10:43.41,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Now that he has Atri-chan to be there for him,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.41,0:10:48.04,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,it feels like Natsu-kun is finally finding his old self again.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.71,0:10:53.34,Default,Yoko,0,0,0,,Why don't we get something to eat?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.88,0:10:54.84,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.17,0:11:00.80,Default,Yoko,0,0,0,,Catherine-sensei said she was gonna eat with Ririka at the school. Wanna drop in?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.26,0:11:03.72,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Yeah. I'd love to!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.14,0:11:06.26,Default,Ryuji,0,0,0,,Oh, count me in too!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.26,0:11:08.98,Default,Yoko,0,0,0,,Yeah, not happening buddy. No boys allowed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.98,0:11:09.73,Default,Yoko,0,0,0,,Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.15,0:11:13.06,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.44,0:11:16.57,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Mom's cooking is served!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.57,0:11:18.15,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,It's just regular nikujaga.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.15,0:11:21.20,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Minamo told me it tastes just like her mom used to make!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.87,0:11:25.66,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,It's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.66,0:11:29.66,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,But of course it is! It was prepared by my high specs!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.66,0:11:31.67,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Cooking comes as easily as breathing for yours truly!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.96,0:11:34.08,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Can't believe you can say that with a straight face.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.08,0:11:39.88,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Why, it's nothing but the truth! While it took me 107 failed tries to perfect my hamburg steak,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.88,0:11:43.72,Default,Atri,0,0,0,TLC,I was able to succeed this time on the mere 74th attempt! {should this be the 74th or 75th?}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.72,0:11:46.56,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,A truly high-spec performance, if I do say so myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.56,0:11:48.56,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,You screwed up {\i1}that{\i0} many times?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.56,0:11:50.56,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,You have nothing to worry about!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.56,0:11:53.52,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Minamo worked her magic on my failures,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.52,0:11:55.90,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,so they all went in our bellies instead of the trash!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.48,0:11:59.11,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,You went through all that just to cook for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.11,0:12:02.90,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Yes! Seeing you enjoy tasty things makes {\i1}me{\i0} happy! {maybe not worth trying to keep this catchphrase, idk how to make it work better}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.45,0:12:05.28,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Why's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.57,0:12:08.29,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Why? Hmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.29,0:12:12.71,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Because it means I'm being useful to you, I guess!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.17,0:12:15.71,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Why does being useful make you happy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.71,0:12:18.84,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Mmm, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.84,0:12:21.34,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Uh, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.17,0:12:24.26,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Oh! I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.26,0:12:25.72,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,It must be love!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.72,0:12:27.10,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Huh? Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.10,0:12:30.18,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,I get it now. It's because I love you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.18,0:12:32.81,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,And not just garden-variety love.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.81,0:12:34.77,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,It's the romantic kind of love!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.86,0:12:40.15,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Sheesh, way to make it sound like I dragged it out of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.15,0:12:41.99,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Is that a bad thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.99,0:12:46.16,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Well, no. If you really meant it, at least...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.74,0:12:52.29,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,I do mean it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.25,0:12:58.13,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,I love you, Natsuki-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.43,0:13:09.47,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,I-I'm starving. And the food's getting cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.06,0:13:12.72,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Nikujaga's way better when it's still hot.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.68,0:13:15.73,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.07,0:13:25.78,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,This is tough... {?}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.32,0:13:30.78,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Do I really love Atri in that way?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.28,0:13:33.12,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,She's the same as she's always been,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.12,0:13:36.79,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,but here I am, projecting that girl from eight years ago onto her...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.04,0:13:41.55,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Actually, wait. She {\i1}is{\i0} that girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.55,0:13:43.38,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,So that means...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.38,0:13:46.26,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,What are you muttering to yourself about?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.68,0:13:52.06,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,H-Hey, what do you think you're wearing...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.51,0:13:56.35,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,You're the one who told me to go and get ready for my bath.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.35,0:13:58.52,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,O-Oh, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.94,0:14:05.32,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Whatever is the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.32,0:14:06.90,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Wh-What're you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.53,0:14:10.12,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Swish.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.49,0:14:15.62,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,I never knew you could scream like that, Natsuki-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.16,0:14:19.12,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Y-You'd better cut that out right now, okay?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.12,0:14:20.21,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Swish!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.04,0:14:24.00,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,And now your face is all red!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.00,0:14:27.22,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,You're giving me all the reactions that I wanted!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.22,0:14:29.55,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,You're so cute that I can't help but want to tease you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.26,0:14:35.06,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,TM,Don't say... I didn't warn you... {possible to do some cute timing effect here or something?}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.44,0:14:43.15,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Robot harassment, I say!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.15,0:14:46.53,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,How dare you hit me, knowing full well that I can't hit you back?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.78,0:14:50.70,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Should've thought about that before trying to sexually harass me, bolts for brains!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.70,0:14:53.33,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,That's still no excuse for violence!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.33,0:14:55.79,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Hmph! It was justified self-defense!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.79,0:14:56.54,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.66,0:14:59.29,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,What am I even looking at?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.29,0:15:01.21,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Catherine gave them to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.21,0:15:04.75,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,She made it very clear to me that I ought to put the "YES" side up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.75,0:15:07.88,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Apparently, I should trust you to be very gentle with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.88,0:15:10.76,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Trust me... to be gentle...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.76,0:15:13.09,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Yes, "a perfect gentleman." Was she wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.44,0:15:22.02,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Am I doing it right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.19,0:15:25.02,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Hell if I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.02,0:15:27.65,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Huh? Wait, come back!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.53,0:15:38.24,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Natsuki-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.73,0:16:06.36,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Being true to my heart, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.77,0:16:07.61,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.23,0:16:11.40,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Get up for a second. I have an idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.20,0:16:16.32,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.74,0:16:17.99,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,That should do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.04,0:16:20.00,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,What's this...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.75,0:16:21.96,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Now the bed is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.96,0:16:24.00,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,You'll be sleeping on this side from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.00,0:16:25.88,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Huh? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.88,0:16:28.46,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,This will only keep me away from you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.46,0:16:30.01,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,That's the plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.01,0:16:31.92,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Heck, this is how it should've been from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.92,0:16:35.93,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Do you not like having me next to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.93,0:16:38.72,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Do you hate me now?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.72,0:16:41.39,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,No. I actually like you quite a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.39,0:16:44.52,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Or, well, I guess "treasure" might be the word I'm looking for.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.61,0:16:54.32,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,As of today, I've decided to start seeing you as a Humanoid with a heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.32,0:16:58.78,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,A real heart, capable of feeling hurt just like any other human's.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.78,0:17:01.29,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,And that's what brought this on?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.75,0:17:02.58,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.29,0:17:06.50,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,The human heart is awfully complex and subtle, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.50,0:17:08.79,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,It's not the sorta thing anyone can understand easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.25,0:17:11.63,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Feelings like love and hate, especially.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.63,0:17:12.76,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.76,0:17:16.80,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,I'm guessing you don't actually understand anything yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.51,0:17:21.74,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,So for now, I just want you to experience more of the joys and sorrows of life
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.22,0:17:24.52,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,so that your heart has time to grow.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.85,0:17:26.64,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Natsuki-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.23,0:17:30.52,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,And maybe then, once you finally understand love
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.52,0:17:33.57,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,and we can both honestly face our feelings,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.57,0:17:36.11,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,then we can decide what comes next for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.16,0:17:40.70,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Um, I'm not sure I understand...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.12,0:17:44.79,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,What exactly are we supposed to do from now on?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.37,0:17:48.25,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Well, to put it simply...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.25,0:17:50.17,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,To put it simply?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.05,0:17:54.67,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Exactly what we've always done.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.68,0:18:06.02,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,What're you looking at, huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.02,0:18:09.56,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,I'm a grown-up. Who gives a rip if I drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.23,0:18:13.48,Default,Yoko,0,0,0,,This is how Catherine-sensei gets when she's drunk?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.48,0:18:15.03,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Yeah, I forgot...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.03,0:18:18.07,Default,Yoko,0,0,0,,You know, I've been wondering, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.07,0:18:20.99,Default,Yoko,0,0,0,,What country is she from, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.99,0:18:22.83,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Japan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.83,0:18:24.93,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Her real name's Hana-chan-sens-
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.10,0:18:26.33,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,Don't call me Hana-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.41,0:18:30.92,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Don't push yourself too hard, okay, Ririka-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.92,0:18:32.88,Default,Ririka,0,0,0,,Push myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.88,0:18:35.71,Default,Ririka,0,0,0,,Nah, I'm just doing it 'cause it's fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.71,0:18:36.92,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.92,0:18:40.01,Default,Ririka,0,0,0,,Yeah. Everyone calls me a hard worker,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.01,0:18:42.30,Default,Ririka,0,0,0,,but I just do it 'cause I like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.64,0:18:47.02,Default,Yoko,0,0,0,,Wow, you don't say. Guess it's all about the mindset, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.02,0:18:48.10,Default,Minamo,0,0,0,,Mm-hmm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.10,0:18:50.98,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,'Swhat makes the heart so hard to understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.56,0:18:52.73,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,This right here...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.36,0:18:56.32,Default,Catherine,0,0,0,,is gonna take some serious thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.99,0:19:01.36,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,This feels strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.70,0:19:04.83,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Is this how everybody sleeps?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.83,0:19:05.95,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,I dunno.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.95,0:19:09.04,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Some people are like this, some aren't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.04,0:19:10.17,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,It's complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.17,0:19:11.37,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.62,0:19:15.00,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Yeah. The human heart is complicated.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.00,0:19:19.51,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,It's not just good and bad, and it's not just right and wrong, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.55,0:19:22.72,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Sometimes, we do the wrong thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.89,0:19:25.43,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,The wrong thing...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.52,0:19:32.56,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Do I really have a heart?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.77,0:19:35.94,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.90,0:19:39.99,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Let's go to sleep already.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.15,0:19:43.07,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.28,0:19:46.62,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,When you said you treasure me,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.62,0:19:48.87,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,it made me really happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.50,0:19:51.50,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Right back at you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.50,0:19:54.79,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,You saved my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.63,0:20:03.30,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,That day, eight years ago, why were you so nice to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.30,0:20:06.39,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,There, there. It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.85,0:20:11.02,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Because... Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.77,0:20:14.81,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,That's what I learned...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.74,0:20:24.45,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,There, there. It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.87,0:20:29.91,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,It hurts... It hurts...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.37,0:20:31.62,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.25,0:20:33.87,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Everything's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.50,0:20:39.00,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,You aren't alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.59,0:20:44.63,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.81,0:20:50.77,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Atri...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.15,0:21:00.23,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Kiss...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.90,0:21:01.94,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.78,0:21:05.70,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Struggled to react,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.70,0:21:09.99,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,but got through the situation by imitating previously-seen reference material.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.99,0:21:14.04,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Natsuki-san seemed to sense nothing amiss.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.04,0:21:17.88,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Natsuki-san said he loves me, so I returned the sentiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.88,0:21:22.67,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,However, his "love" differed from my hypothesis.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.67,0:21:24.63,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Learned about romantic love.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.63,0:21:26.68,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Searched for relevant material.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.68,0:21:27.64,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,What the...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.64,0:21:29.47,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Learned about kissing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.47,0:21:31.22,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Learned about sexual intercourse.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.22,0:21:35.48,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Learned about courtship rituals and methods to lead into intercourse.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.48,0:21:38.60,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Natsuki-san suspects nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.52,0:21:41.57,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Replied that I have a heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.71,0:21:57.58,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Natsuki-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.37,0:21:59.29,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Stay away.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.75,0:22:00.54,Default,Atri,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.38,0:22:03.76,Default,Natsuki,0,0,0,,Stay away from me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.76,0:22:06.76,Default,,0,0,0,,
